  <release>
    <version>1.0.3</version>
    <date>2006-02-22</date>
    <notes>* Fix cell width calculation if setting header with associative array (Bug 4299).
* Fix fatal reference error with some PHP versions (Bug 5309).
* Fix notice if no data has been provided (Bug 5851).
* Added multibyte support (Requests 2934 and 7014).</notes>
    <state>stable</state>
    <filelist>
